l.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1511%2c20220818%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,1511,20220818,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1511","JDATE":"20220818","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}